{{Infobox government agency |agency_name = Ministry of Agriculture of the Republic of Lithuania |type = [[Ministry (collective executive)|Ministry]] |nativename = Lietuvos Respublikos žemės ūkio ministerija |nativename_a = |nativename_r = |logo = Ministry of Agriculture of the Republic of Lithuania logo.gif |logo_width = |logo_caption = |seal = |seal_width = |seal_caption = |picture = Žemės ūkio ministerija ir žemės ūkio biblioteka.JPG |picture_width = |picture_caption = |formed = {{Start date|1918|11}} |preceding1 = |preceding2 = <!-- (etc.) --> |dissolved = |superseding = |jurisdiction = |headquarters = [[Vilnius]], [[Lithuania]] |coordinates = |employees = |budget = |minister1_name = [[Giedrius Surplys]] |minister1_pfo = |minister2_name = |minister2_pfo = <!-- (etc.) --> |deputyminister1_name = |deputyminister1_pfo = |deputyminister2_name = |deputyminister2_pfo = <!-- (etc.) --> |chief1_name = |chief1_position = |chief2_name = |chief2_position = <!-- (etc.) --> |agency_type = |parent_department = |parent_agency = |child1_agency = |child2_agency = <!-- (etc.) --> |keydocument1= <!-- (etc.) --> |website = {{URL|www.zum.lt}} |footnotes = |map = |map_width = |map_caption = }}
The '''Ministry of Agriculture of the Republic of Lithuania''' ({{lang-lt|Lietuvos Respublikos žemės ūkio ministerija}}) is a [[government department]] of the Republic of [[Lithuania]]. Its operations are authorized by the [[Constitution of the Republic of Lithuania]], decrees issued by the [[President of Lithuania|President]] and [[Prime Minister of Lithuania|Prime Minister]], and laws passed by the [[Seimas]] (Parliament). Its mission is to prosecute state policy realization and coordination in ranges of land, food, fishery, village development, agriculture.<ref>[http://www.zum.lt/en Ministry of Agriculture of the Republic of Lithuania]</ref> The current head of the Ministry is [[Giedrius Surplys]].
